description: This is a simple skill to allow you to ask Alexa to tell you some interesting fitness facts.  The goal of this skill is to give you advice on how to live a healthy, productive lifestyle.
exampleInteractions: Alexa, tell fit assist to give me some health advice
Alexa, tell fit assist to give me a fit fact
Alexa, ask fit assist to tell me a fitness fact
name: Fit Assist
